We have an exciting opportunity for an Embryologist who is passionate about
reproductive science and exceptional patient care.

Working collaboratively with our friendly and supportive team, you will
perform a range of standard and complex procedures, using advanced equipment
in our laboratory at Greenslopes Private Hospital.

You will be available to work from 6:30am or 7:30am Monday to Friday, public
holidays and weekend rotating rosters.

** Responsibilities **

  * Perform standard ART procedures and other treatments undertaken in the andrology/embryology laboratory; 
  * Perform (or develop proficiency in) a range of advanced ART procedures; 
  * Provide scientific support at clinical procedures; 
  * Participate in quality management and audit processes; 

** Requirements: **

  * Experience working in a clinical andrology/embryology laboratory; 
  * Bachelor of Science degree or equivalent; 
  * Demonstrated competency at standard ART procedures (including embryo transfer and vitrification) and ICSI experience (essential); 
  * Experience in embryo biopsy is preferred but not essential; 
  * Knowledge of ART legislation and clinical protocols; 
  * Knowledge of RTAC Code of Practice and Pathology Practice and Accreditation (NATA) 
  * Knowledge of quality management and aseptic technique. 

** Attributes: **

  * Excellent communication, organisational and inventory skills; 
  * Accuracy and attention to detail; 
  * A team player with the ability to work autonomously; 
  * Ability to follow policies and procedures without supervision; 
  * Computer literacy and keyboard skills. 

For further information please contact HR via email: [ [email protected]
](/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#f19983b19887979c9495df929e9cdf9084) . Please
apply online including your CV and a cover letter. All applications are
treated with strict confidence.

Care Fertility offers ART services guided by the latest research in a warm,
friendly environment and with a personalised approach to patient care. Our
services include artificial insemination, IVF and ICSI, IMSI, PGT, time lapse
incubation, semen analysis, cryopreservation of gametes and embryos and known
donor egg and sperm cycles. Our boutique fertility unit is located in
Greenslopes Private Hospital.

